## Project Structure

```
llm_calibration_eval/
├── __init__.py          # Exports Evaluator, EvaluationResult
├── __main__.py          # python -m llm_calibration_eval entry point
├── cli.py               # Argument parsing & CLI commands
├── evaluator.py         # Orchestration: Evaluator, EvaluationResult
├── providers/
│   ├── base.py          # LLMProvider ABC, ProviderResponse, CalibrationSample
│   ├── mock_provider.py # Deterministic mock (no API key needed)
│   ├── openai_provider.py
│   └── anthropic_provider.py
├── metrics/
│   ├── brier.py         # Brier score & Brier Skill Score
│   ├── ece.py           # ECE & MCE
│   └── reliability.py   # Reliability diagram data (ReliabilityBin)
├── datasets/
│   └── trivia.py        # 50 trivia Q&A with known answers
└── calibration/
    └── temperature_scaling.py  # Post-hoc calibration via learned T
tests/
├── test_metrics.py
├── test_providers.py
└── test_evaluator.py
```

